Package: scReportComposition
Type: Package
Title: Single-Cell Composition Interactive HTML Report Generator
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Kee-gong Karios",
                  family = "Park",
                  email = "karioslion0517@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Generate self-contained interactive HTML reports from single-cell
    RNA-seq cell composition results. Accepts Seurat objects and produces a
    composition table with stacked bar plots, cell-type fraction distributions,
    and summary statistics. Designed as a lightweight companion to scReportLite
    in the scReport ecosystem.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    plotly,
    htmltools,
    jsonlite
Suggests:
    Seurat,
    SeuratObject
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
